tool_tip_prefix:
<style type="text/css" media="screen">
body {
  background: transparent;
/*  opacity: 0.9;*/
}
html,body,table{font-size:10px; font-family: "Lucida Grande", "Trebuchet MS", Verdana, sans-serif;}
table{-webkit-border-radius:1ex;background-color:#fff;border:2px solid #eee;width:auto;}
td.declaration{width:15em;}
td.comp{-webkit-border-radius:1ex;}

/*COMPATIBILITY TABLES*/
table.compatibility{line-height:140%;border-spacing:0.5em;position:relative;}
table.compatibility caption{border-top:1px dotted #9198C1;padding:10px 0;text-align:left;}
table.compatibility caption select{margin-left:5px;margin-right:7px;border:1px dotted #9198C1;}
wbr:after{content:"00B"}
tr{width:100%;}
table.compatibility ul,table.compatibility ol{border:none;margin-bottom:0;}
table.compatibility td{vertical-align:top;}
col.IE{width:3em;}
col.FF{width:4em;}
col.Saf{width:4em;}
col.Op{width:4em;}
col.Rest{width:8em;}
tr.compheader{background-color:#F2F3EF;}
tr.compheader th{font-weight:normal;font-size:90%;color:#666666;}
tr.compheader th:first-child{text-align:right;padding:1em;}
tr.compheader:last-child th{border:none;}
td.header{background-color:#F2F3EF;padding:0.3em;}
td.header h3,td.header h4{margin-top:0.5em;text-align:center;}
td.declaration{background-color:#F2F3EF;text-align:right;padding-right:10px;color:#666666;}
td.declaration a{text-decoration:none;}
div.name{font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:1em;margin-top:1em;}
td.comp{font-family:verdana,sans-serif;font-size:95%;text-transform:lowercase;text-align:center;height:3em;vertical-align:middle !important;}
table.keepCaps td.comp{text-transform:none;}
td.yes{background-color:#00882D;color:#ffffff;text-shadow:0 1px 1px #003211;}
td.almost{background-color:#40A662;color:#ffffff;text-shadow:0 1px 1px #297D47;}
td.incomplete{color:#00882D;border:1px solid #00882D;}
td.alternative{color:#666666;border:1px solid #666666;}
td.untestable{color:#006699;}
td.minimal{color:#CB000F;}
td.incorrect{color:#CB000F;border:1px solid #CB000F;}
td.inappropriate{background-color:#EFB2B7;text-shadow:0 1px 1px #fff;}
td.toomany{background-color:#CCE7D5;text-shadow:0 1px 1px #fff;}
td.buggy{background-color:#DA4C57;color:#ffffff;text-shadow:0 1px 1px #81272C;}
td.severebug{background-color:#82000A;color:#ffffff;text-shadow:0 1px 1px #410005;}
td.no{background-color:#CB000F;color:#ffffff;text-shadow:0 1px 1px #410301;}
td.crash{background-color:#535353;font-weight:bold;text-transform:uppercase;color:#ffffff;text-shadow:0 1px 1px #333;}
b.warning{display:block;color:#F2F3EF;padding:0.5em;margin-right:-10px;margin-top:0.5em;background-color:#999999;text-shadow:0 1px 1px #666;}
td pre{padding:0;}
td pre + p{margin-top:2px;}
td th,td td{padding:1px !important;vertical-align:top;color:#666666;}
td th{text-align:left !important;}

cite {
  -webkit-transition: right 1s ease-out, opacity 1s ease-out;
  position: relative;
  opacity: 0;
  right: 50%;
  
  display: block;
  float: right;
  -webkit-border-radius: 1ex;
  margin: 1ex auto 0;
  text-align: center;
  background: #111;
  color: #eee;
  line-height: 2em;
  padding: 0 1em;
  text-shadow: 0 1px 1px #000;
  border: 1px solid #222;
}
</style>
<script>
window.addEventListener('load',function(){
  
  var c = document.getElementsByTagName('cite')[0];
  c.style.right = '0px';
  c.style.opacity = '1';
  
},false);
</script>
